<HEADLINE> 1,000 Bangladeshi Refugees Return Home From India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, February 2 (Xinhua) -- Some 1,025 Bangladeshi tribal
refugees returned home Monday from refugee camps in the Indian
state of Tripura, the country's national news agency BSS reported.
</P>
<P>
