</P>
<P>
This is the first ever visit by an Argentinean head of state to
Lebanon.
</P>
<P>
During his three-day stay, he will meet his Lebanese
counterpart Elias Hrawi and other senior officials on the
situation in the south and the bilateral economic ties.
</P>
<P>
