displayers, electric heaters, capacitors and acoustic appliances
exceeded 100 million U.S. dollars each last year. TV sets,
vessels, clocks and watches, automobiles, motorcycles, bicycles,
motors, and electric generators reached more than 50 million
U.S. dollars each.
</P>
<P>
A provincial official said that Fujian has over the years
formulated a number of preferential policies to encourage overseas
investment in the sectors of machinery and electronics. Last year
overseas-funded enterprises accounted for 73.5 percent of Fujian's
total exports of machinery and electronics.  
