Trade unions of the workers said Monday that the strike will
continue indefinitely till their demand is met.
</P>
<P>
The unions want the 23 management companies under the EFC to
raise the daily salary for workers from 83 Rupees (1.34
U.S. dollars) to 103 Rupees (1.66 dollars). However, the EFC only
agrees to offer 93 Rupees (1.5 dollars). (Sri Lanka-Strike)
</P>
